---

<div class="urgency-bar">
  <div class="container inner">
    <span class="label">Regulatory update</span>
    <p>
      The EU AI Act's high-risk provisions are already enforceable. Organisations using AI in HR,
      credit, healthcare, or customer-facing systems may already be in breach.
      <a href="/services">Does your organisation know which category it falls into?</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .urgency-bar {
    background-color: rgba(0, 28, 59, 0.96);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(53, 147, 255, 0.25);
    padding-block: 0.85rem;
  }

  .inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  p a {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  p a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
